            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>enchilada filling</strong> between your <strong>tortillas</strong></p><p>Roll up each<strong> tortilla</strong> <strong>tightly</strong> and place them in an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> enchilada topping </strong>and<strong> torn cheese flavour slices</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 12-15 min or until the tortillas are crispy and the cheeze has melted – these are your<strong> lighter cheezy chipotle chicken enchiladas</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
